{"nodes":[{"pos":[12,49],"content":"Compiler Error C2034 | Microsoft Docs","needQuote":false,"needEscape":true,"nodes":[{"content":"Compiler Error C2034 | Microsoft Docs","pos":[0,37]}]},{"content":"Compiler Error C2034","pos":[597,617]},{"content":"'identifier' : type of bit field too small for number of bits","pos":[618,679]},{"content":"The number of bits in the bit-field declaration exceeds the size of the base type.","pos":[686,768]},{"content":"The following sample generates C2034:","pos":[775,812]},{"content":"Possible resolution:","pos":[915,935]}],"content":"---\ntitle: \"Compiler Error C2034 | Microsoft Docs\"\nms.custom: \"\"\nms.date: \"11/04/2016\"\nms.reviewer: \"\"\nms.suite: \"\"\nms.technology: \n  - \"devlang-cpp\"\nms.tgt_pltfrm: \"\"\nms.topic: \"error-reference\"\nf1_keywords: \n  - \"C2034\"\ndev_langs: \n  - \"C++\"\nhelpviewer_keywords: \n  - \"C2034\"\nms.assetid: 953d70fa-bde9-4ce6-a55d-741e7bc63ff4\ncaps.latest.revision: 7\nauthor: \"corob-msft\"\nms.author: \"corob\"\nmanager: \"ghogen\"\ntranslation.priority.ht: \n  - \"cs-cz\"\n  - \"de-de\"\n  - \"es-es\"\n  - \"fr-fr\"\n  - \"it-it\"\n  - \"ja-jp\"\n  - \"ko-kr\"\n  - \"pl-pl\"\n  - \"pt-br\"\n  - \"ru-ru\"\n  - \"tr-tr\"\n  - \"zh-cn\"\n  - \"zh-tw\"\n---\n# Compiler Error C2034\n'identifier' : type of bit field too small for number of bits  \n  \n The number of bits in the bit-field declaration exceeds the size of the base type.  \n  \n The following sample generates C2034:  \n  \n```  \n// C2034.cpp  \nstruct A {  \n   char test : 9;   // C2034, char has 8 bits  \n};  \n```  \n  \n Possible resolution:  \n  \n```  \n// C2034b.cpp  \n// compile with: /c  \nstruct A {  \n   char test : 8;  \n};  \n```"}